				<div class="justify-content-between" style="font-size:150%;">
					<span class="font-weight-bold;">Zippity</span>
					<span class="text-muted" style="font-style:italic;">Clever • Affectionate • Gentle</span>
				</div>

				<hr class="my-3">

				<!-- SUMMARY ------------------------------------->

				<p>Zip is a gentle companion to AJ ferret who purchased her directly from the pillowing artisan who crafted her. Seems this little character was nervous to appear in the shop for customers, but because AJ does nothing but lounge around the shop she had the unique experience to get to know the dragonfly pillowing. After seeing the bond they formed, the artisan agreed to sell to AJ.
<br><br>
Zippity and AJ have been pretty inseperable since! Zip gets along with all of the other pillowings in AJ's busy household. Even the large ones! Seems that little Zip has an irrational fear of being eaten by a bigger pillowing. She's been sat on more than once and did not enjoy the experience.
<br><br>
Some of Zip's favorite play dates are with other flying kit pillowings. Being able to frolic and chase each other through the air seems to be a highlight to everyone's day. As much fun as it looks, it's just as much fun to kick back and watch!</p>

				<!-- LIKES / DISLIKES ------------------------------------->

